All blog tags are not fetched by the blog_tags function, how can we solved this?

I'm using this code for fetch the list of all blog tags

{% set my_tags = blog_tags("default", 250) %}
&lt;ul&gt;
{% for item in my_tags %}
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="{{ blog_tag_url(group.id, item.slug) }}"&gt;{{ item }}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
{% endfor %}
&lt;/ul&gt;

when i preview the module just show the 4 tags in a list and total tags is 80
